# Runtime state directory for the docker compose stack.
#
# Populated at runtime:
#   registry.sqlite           SQLite registry (rebuildable from artifacts/)
#   registry.sqlite-wal       WAL sidecar
#   registry.sqlite-shm       shared-memory sidecar
#   audit_chain.jsonl         append-only audit log
#   artifacts/                canonical soul + constitution tree
#   soul_generated/           daemon-written new souls/constitutions
#   ollama/                   (when using --profile llm) Ollama model cache
#
# On first boot of the daemon container, ./artifacts is seeded from the
# /app/examples tree inside the image. Subsequent boots leave user data
# alone — see scripts/docker-entrypoint.sh.
#
# All of these are .gitignore'd except this placeholder.
